===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro}} {{term|hermine|lang=fro}}, either from {{ML.}} {{term|mus|mūs|lang=la}} {{term|Armenius|lang=la}} ("Armenian mouse"), from where its fur was exported, or a modification of a Germanic word.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/'ɜːmɪn/}}
* {{rhymes|ɜː(r)mɪn}}

